name: UnauthorizedAmericanFamilyFitnessSchedules
0:
”Alexa, ask gym class helper to get today's schedule”
”Alexa, ask gym class helper for the schedule at midlothian on Friday”
”Alexa, ask gym class helper what is today's schedule at Short Pump”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gym class helper
des:
Get Alexa to list all classes (currently just the Power class). Request can be made for a specific gym location and/or on a particular day. 

The results will tell you how many classes, along with the time the class occurs and the name of the instructor teaching the class.

This skill is NOT authorized by American Family Fitness and is just a fan skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
